{"tid":269796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"把煙火當爆炸！歐冠聯賽決賽 球迷踩踏釀200傷","createTime":"2017-06-04T00:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T01:29:33.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0359ee437a07c3c077de21e5d192854cddd2b74d","tid":269796,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"把煙火當爆炸！歐冠聯賽決賽 球迷踩踏釀200傷<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZA8hpB-ScYE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZA8hpB-ScYE&d=Fiz9sUK44yqC5LGHjQNXzgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=e4de3c5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZA8hpB-ScYE</a><br />\n義大利足球隊祖雲達斯（Juventus）對上西班牙皇家馬德里的歐冠決賽中，突發巨響，引起在義大利聖卡洛廣場（Piazza San Carlo）觀賽的球迷恐慌，不少人遭推倒踩傷，估約200人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，比賽前10分鐘有人施放煙火，現場傳出巨響，當時在觀賽的球迷以為恐攻，開始驚慌逃竄，互相推擠、踩踏，使現場陷入混亂，尖叫聲此起彼落，有不少球迷因此濺血受傷。<br />\n<br />\n現場民眾向記者表示，聽到爆炸聲後，大家拚了命地想逃離廣場，不少孩子、父母被人潮沖散，「過了數分鐘後，我們心有餘悸，那個聲音真的像炸彈爆炸」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170604000930-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170604000930-260408&d=Fiz9sUK44yqC5LGHjQNXzgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=31eb9904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170604000930-260408</a>"},{"pid":"51e7c27ff087d22c213c1056a46a3a18209c87c6","tid":269796,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/084259_34597865f1057e57ffc2b800ff0213de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F084259_34597865f1057e57ffc2b800ff0213de.jpg&h=9362d5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/084300_48ad85331caa2663390aa4971d4037c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F084300_48ad85331caa2663390aa4971d4037c1.jpg&h=877cfa5c&s={SIZE